      • parse

        public abstract org.openimaj.util.pair.IndependentPair<String,List<URL>> parse(String data)
                                                                        throws Exception
        Parse a record into a key and list of potential URLs. In most cases there will only be a single potential URL in the list. The downloader will work through the list until it finds a working URL, or exhausts its options.
        Parameters:
        data - the data record from the input file
        Returns:
        the key and potential URLs
        Throws:
        Exception - if an error occurs
